{"@context":"http://iiif.io/api/presentation/3/context.json","id":"https://digbmc.github.io/pta-manifests/phan/phan-15123/manifest.json","type":"Manifest","label":{"none":["PHAN-15123"]},"metadata":[{"label":{"none":["Timestamp"]},"value":{"none":["1:51:23"]}},{"label":{"none":["Film"]},"value":{"none":["Phantom Thread"]}},{"label":{"none":["Distance"]},"value":{"none":["medium shot"]}},{"label":{"none":["Angle"]},"value":{"none":["low"]}},{"label":{"none":["Location"]},"value":{"none":["interior"]}},{"label":{"none":["Movement"]},"value":{"none":["fixed"]}},{"label":{"none":["Composition"]},"value":{"none":["two shot"]}}],"summary":{"none":["Man angrily turns his head toward woman behind him"]},"thumbnail":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-15123/tiles/full/300,169/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":169,"width":300}],"homepage":[{"id":"PHAN-15123","type":"Text","format":"text/html","label":{"none":["Object homepage"]}}],"items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-15123/canvas/1","type":"Canvas","height":1080,"width":1920,"label":{"none":["PHAN-15123"]},"thumbnail":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-15123/tiles/full/300,169/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":169,"width":300}],"items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-15123/canvas/1/annopage-1","type":"AnnotationPage","items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-15123/canvas/1/annopage-1/anno-1","type":"Annotation","motivation":"painting","target":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-15123/canvas/1","body":{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-15123/tiles/full/1920,1080/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":1080,"width":1920,"service":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-15123/tiles","type":"ImageService3","profile":"http://iiif.io/api/image/3/level0.json"}]}}]}],"annotations":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-15123/canvas/1/page/p1","type":"AnnotationPage","items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-15123/canvas/1/bdbb5147-98b0-4ce8-9092-9e5cd73ce283","type":"Annotation","motivation":"commenting","body":[{"created":"2026-07-01T18:46:00.824Z","creator":"Ada ","purpose":"commenting","type":"TextualBody","format":"text/html","value":"<p>Alma and Cyril speak over Reynolds’s head, almost as if he is not in the room, discussing professional matters and maintaining their composure even as he reacts explosively. They both now respect each other, professionally and personally, outside of their relations to him. Their calm makes his outburst seem particularly childish and unprofessional, and underscores the ways that the two women, not Reynolds, hold the power over their household.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>"}],"target":{"type":"SpecificResource","source":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-15123/canvas/1","selector":{"type":"FragmentSelector","conformsTo":"http://www.w3.org/TR/media-frags/","value":"xywh=pixel:1346.3246417197452,128.0538415605095,413.0545879777069,385.73347929936307"}}},{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-15123/canvas/1/7d94af0f-c6da-40f6-935d-dcaa2087cc6f","type":"Annotation","motivation":"commenting","body":[{"created":"2026-07-01T18:46:21.478Z","creator":"Ada ","purpose":"commenting","type":"TextualBody","format":"text/html","value":"<p>In this framing, Alma hovers over Reynolds’s left shoulder. As Reynolds confesses to Cyril that he regrets marrying Alma, the latter’s position in the shot composition reflects his sense of how she has turned his life upside-down and intruded into his home.&nbsp;</p>"}],"target":{"type":"SpecificResource","source":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-15123/canvas/1","selector":{"type":"FragmentSelector","conformsTo":"http://www.w3.org/TR/media-frags/","value":"xywh=pixel:661.4764132165606,197.2735867834395,1065.4426253980891,505.9611365445859"}}}]}]}]}